        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 1:56AM CDT until June 8 at 2:30AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 155 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles east of
Adrian, or 7 miles northwest of Vega, moving southeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Vega, Adrian, and Wildorado.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
